  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2023-03-16",
    "date": "2023-06-14T18:20:44Z",
    "text": "Sunshine in the Courtroom Act of 2023\n\nThis bill establishes a framework to allow federal court proceedings\u2014in district courts, in circuit courts, and at the Supreme Court\u2014to be photographed, recorded, broadcast, or televised. Specifically, it authorizes the presiding judge to permit media coverage of court proceedings, subject to requirements and limitations."
